{
  "chapter": 2,
  "chapter_summary": "丁鹏被两个神秘老人（梅花老人与墨竹子）用绳索吊在树上，二人下完棋后离去。绳断后丁鹏前往万松山庄赴约，却被门房告知柳若松已外出，需等到下月十五。丁鹏身无分文，饥寒交迫，回到当初遇见神秘女子的地方，竟再次遇见她。女子自称李可笑，二人互诉心意。可笑让丁鹏前往溪边一座绿瓦小楼，小楼主人正是可笑本人。丁鹏沐浴更衣，与可笑共度一夜。临别时丁鹏将藏有天外流星剑谱的裤带赠予可笑。丁鹏苦练数日后，于七月十五重返万松山庄。柳若松请来点苍钟展、岁寒三友中的梅花老人与墨竹子，以及神剑山庄管事谢先生作为见证。丁鹏与柳若松即将展开比武。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_hua_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "梅花老人",
      "listener": "char_mo_zhu_zi",
      "text": "你不能走，我们一定还得下一盘。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 37
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_men_fang",
      "speaker_name": "门房",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "丁少爷来得实在太早了，今天还是十五，还没有到十六，我们庄主和庄上请来的那些朋友，本来应该在这里等丁少爷来的，就算等上个三天五天，实在也算不了什么。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 97,
      "line_end": 99
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_men_fang",
      "text": "我本来早就……",
      "tone": "慎重",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 101,
      "line_end": 101
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_men_fang",
      "speaker_name": "门房",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "只可惜我们庄主今天恰巧有点事，一定要赶到城里去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 103,
      "line_end": 105
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_men_fang",
      "speaker_name": "门房",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "我们庄主再三吩咐我，一定要请丁少爷恩罪，因为他只等了三个时辰，就有事出去了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 107,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是我怎么办？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 115,
      "line_end": 115
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_men_fang",
      "text": "我能够在这里等他回来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 123,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_men_fang",
      "speaker_name": "门房",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "丁少爷如果要肯在这里等，当然也可以！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 125,
      "line_end": 125
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_men_fang",
      "speaker_name": "门房",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "但是我们都不敢让丁少爷留下来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 127,
      "line_end": 129
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_men_fang",
      "speaker_name": "门房",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "因为庄主这一出去，至少要在外面呆上二三十天，我们怎敢让丁少爷在这里等上二三十天！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 131,
      "line_end": 133
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_men_fang",
      "speaker_name": "门房",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "但是庄主也关照过，下个月十五之前一定会回来，那时候他就没事了，就是等个三五天也没关系。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 137,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_men_fang",
      "text": "好，我下个月十五再来，正午之前一定来。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 141,
      "line_end": 141
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_men_fang",
      "speaker_name": "门房",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "我说过，庄主那天没事，丁少爷晚点来也没关系。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 143,
      "line_end": 143
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "text": "是你！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 203,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "可笑",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "我本来以为永远见不到你了。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 215,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "text": "我本来以为永远见不到你了。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 215,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "可笑",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "刚才我一直在提醒自己，这次如果能见到你，一定要记住一件事。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 223,
      "line_end": 225
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 227,
      "line_end": 227
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "可笑",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "记住问你的名字。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 229,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "text": "你是说可笑？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 235,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "可笑",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "嗯！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 237,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "text": "可以的可，笑话的笑？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 239,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "可笑",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "嗯！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 241,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "text": "这个名字真奇怪。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 243,
      "line_end": 243
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "可笑",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "不仅奇怪，而且可笑，再加上我的姓更可笑。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 245,
      "line_end": 245
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "text": "你姓什么？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 247,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "可笑",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "姓李。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 249,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "可笑",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "一个人的名字居然叫李可笑，你说可笑不可笑？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 251,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "可笑",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "我真想不通，我爸爸怎么会替我取这么样一个名字的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 255,
      "line_end": 255
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "text": "其实这名字也没什么不好。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 257,
      "line_end": 257
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "可笑",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "但是从小就有人问我：'李可笑，你有什么可笑？'我一听见别人问我这句话，我的头就大了，哪里还笑得出。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 259,
      "line_end": 261
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "可笑",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "我知道你一定想问我，为什么要你去找那个穿红衭裳的老头子？为什么没有在这里等你？这半天到什么地方去了？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 287,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "可笑",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "但是你最好不要问。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 293,
      "line_end": 293
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 295,
      "line_end": 295
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "可笑",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "因为你就算问我，我也不会说的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 297,
      "line_end": 297
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "可笑",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "有些事你还是不要知道的好，一个人知道的事越多，烦恼也就越多，我不想给你再添烦恼。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 299,
      "line_end": 301
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "text": "我听你的话，你不说，我就不问。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 309,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "可笑",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "但是我还是要你去替我做一件事。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 311,
      "line_end": 311
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 313,
      "line_end": 313
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "可笑",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "沿着这条溪水往下走，有个屋顶上铺着绿瓦的小楼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 315,
      "line_end": 315
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "text": "你要我到那里去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 317,
      "line_end": 317
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "可笑",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "我要你现在就去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 319,
      "line_end": 319
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "text": "然后呢？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 321,
      "line_end": 321
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "可笑",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你到了那里之后，就会有人带你去见那里的主人，他说的话你一定要听，他要你做的事你一定要做。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 323,
      "line_end": 325
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "可笑",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你一定要信任我，我绝不会害你的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 327,
      "line_end": 327
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "text": "我相信。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 329,
      "line_end": 329
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "可笑",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你去不去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 331,
      "line_end": 331
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姓娘",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你找谁？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 361,
      "line_end": 363
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "我找这里的主人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 365,
      "line_end": 365
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姓娘",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "我带你去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 367,
      "line_end": 367
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "可笑",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "是谁要你来找我的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 377,
      "line_end": 379
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "text": "是一位李姓娘。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 381,
      "line_end": 381
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "可笑",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "她是你的什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 383,
      "line_end": 383
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "text": "是我的朋友。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 385,
      "line_end": 385
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "可笑",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "她跟你说了些什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 387,
      "line_end": 387
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "text": "她说你要我做的事，我就得去做。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 389,
      "line_end": 389
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "可笑",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你听她的话？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 391,
      "line_end": 391
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "text": "我相信她绝不会害我。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 393,
      "line_end": 393
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "可笑",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "不管我要你做什么，你都肯做？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 395,
      "line_end": 395
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "text": "你是她的朋友，我也信任你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 397,
      "line_end": 397
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "可笑",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你知不知道我要对你怎么样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 399,
      "line_end": 399
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 401,
      "line_end": 401
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "可笑",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "我要把你按进一盆很烫很烫的热水里，用一把大刷子把你身上的泥全部刷下来，用一套你从来没有穿过的那种衣服套在你身上，用一双新鞋子套住你的脚，再把你按在椅子上。用一锅已经炖了好几个时辰的牛腰肉把你的肚子塞满，让你走都走不动。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 403,
      "line_end": 407
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "text": "我对你不错，你为什么要这样子害我？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 415,
      "line_end": 415
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "可笑",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "谁叫你这么听话的，我不害你害谁？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 417,
      "line_end": 417
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "text": "其实这些事我都不怕。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 419,
      "line_end": 419
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "可笑",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你怕什么？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 421,
      "line_end": 421
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "text": "我最怕喝酒，如果你再用几斤陈年的绍兴酒来灌我，就真的害苦我了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 423,
      "line_end": 425
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "可笑",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "现在，你总该知道，你实在不该对我太好的，因为，对我越好的人，我反而越想要害他。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 441,
      "line_end": 443
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "text": "其实我也不能算对你很好，我只不过给了你一件破衣服，请你吃了一点冷牛肉，冷馝头而已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 445,
      "line_end": 447
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "可笑",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你给我的并不是一件破衣服，而是你所有的衣服，你请我吃的也不是一点牛肉，而是你所有的粮食。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 449,
      "line_end": 451
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "可笑",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "如果有个人把他所有的一切全都给了你，你会怎么样对他？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 453,
      "line_end": 455
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "可笑",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "如果有个人把他所有的一切都给了我，我只有一个法子对他。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 461,
      "line_end": 463
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "text": "什么法子？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 465,
      "line_end": 465
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "可笑",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "我也会把我所有的一切都给他。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 467,
      "line_end": 467
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "text": "你知不知道我在想什么？",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 483,
      "line_end": 483
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "可笑",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你在想什么？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 485,
      "line_end": 485
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "text": "我在想，如果我是个又有钱，又有名的人，我一定会带你去游遍天下，让天下所有的人都羡慕我们，嫉忌我们，那时你一定也会为我而觉得骄傲的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 487,
      "line_end": 489
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "text": "可惜现在我只不过是个什么都没有的穷小子。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 491,
      "line_end": 491
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "可笑",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "我喜欢的就是你这个穷小子。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 493,
      "line_end": 493
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "text": "我忘了，我还有样东西可以给你。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 495,
      "line_end": 495
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "text": "我要把这条裤带给你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 497,
      "line_end": 499
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "可笑",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "只要是你给我的，我一定会好好地保存。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 505,
      "line_end": 505
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "text": "我不要你好好保存它，我要你把它剪开来。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 507,
      "line_end": 507
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "可笑",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "这一招真的有这么厉害？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 519,
      "line_end": 519
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "text": "本来我也没把握的，还不敢找真正的高手来试，可是现在我已知道，青城、华山和嵩阳的剑法遇着这一招，简直就好像豆腐遇见了快刀一样，完全没有抵抗之力。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 523,
      "line_end": 524
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "text": "等我击败了柳若松，我就会去找比他更有名的人，总有一天，我会要江湖中所有成名的剑客都败在我的剑下，那时候我就会觉得和神剑山庄谢家的三少爷一样有名。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 527,
      "line_end": 529
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "可笑",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "这是你最珍贵的东西，我不能要。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 531,
      "line_end": 531
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "text": "我就是要把我最珍贵的东西送给你，你为什么不要？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 535,
      "line_end": 535
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "可笑",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "我是个女人，我并不想跟江湖中那些成名的剑客去争强斗胜，只要你有这个心，我已经很高兴了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 537,
      "line_end": 539
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "可笑",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "我只想要你这个人。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 541,
      "line_end": 541
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "可笑",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "我记得你七月十五还有个约会。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 547,
      "line_end": 547
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "text": "到了那一天，我会去的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 549,
      "line_end": 549
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "可笑",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "今天已经是初八了，这几天你应该去练练剑，最好能一个人到别的地方去练，我知道你一看见我，就会……就会想的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 551,
      "line_end": 553
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_li_ke_xiao",
      "text": "我现在就在想。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 555,
      "line_end": 555
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "有几位朋友久慕丁少爷的剑法，想来观摩观摩，我就自作主张，请他们来了，只希望丁少爷不要怪罪。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 609,
      "line_end": 611
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "来的是些什么人？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 617,
      "line_end": 617
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "一位是武林中的前辈，点苍山的钟老先生。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 619,
      "line_end": 619
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "风云剑客钟展！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 621,
      "line_end": 621
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "想不到丁少爷也知道这位老先生。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 623,
      "line_end": 623
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "梅花老人和墨竹子也会来，江湖中把我们平列为岁寒三友，其实我是绝不敢当的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 629,
      "line_end": 629
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "还有一位谢先生，在江湖中的名气并不大，因为他很少在外面走动。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 633,
      "line_end": 633
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "神剑山庄中的人，一向都很少在江湖中走动的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 637,
      "line_end": 637
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "神剑山庄？这位谢先生是神剑山庄中的人？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 639,
      "line_end": 639
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 641,
      "line_end": 641
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "晚辈丁鹏，求前辈赐招，但望前辈剑下留情。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 696,
      "line_end": 698
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_zhan",
      "speaker_name": "钟展",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你还年轻，有件事你一定要永远记住。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 700,
      "line_end": 700
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_zhong_zhan",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 702,
      "line_end": 702
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_zhan",
      "speaker_name": "钟展",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "剑本是无情之物，只要剑一出锄，就留不得情的。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 704,
      "line_end": 706
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "谢先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好剑。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 712,
      "line_end": 712
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "舍下还有口剑，虽然不是什么神兵利器，也还过得去，丁少爷如果不嫌弃我就叫人去拿来。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 726,
      "line_end": 728
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "晚辈就用这柄剑，这是先父的遗物，晚辈不敢轻弃。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 732,
      "line_end": 733
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "丁少爷的剑法，也是家传的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 736,
      "line_end": 736
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 738,
      "line_end": 738
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_zhan",
      "speaker_name": "钟展",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你是太湖丁家的子弟？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 740,
      "line_end": 740
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_zhong_zhan",
      "text": "晚辈是冀北人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 742,
      "line_end": 742
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_zhan",
      "speaker_name": "钟展",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "就怪了。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 744,
      "line_end": 744
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_zhan",
      "speaker_name": "钟展",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "江湖传言，都说这位丁少爷不仅剑法奇高，最有成就的那一剑，更如天外飞来，神奇妙绝，我学剑五十年，竟不知道冀北还有个丁家，竟有如此精妙的家传剑法。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 746,
      "line_end": 748
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "谢先生",
      "listener": "char_zhong_zhan",
      "text": "其实这也没有什么奇怪的，江湖之中，本就有很多不求闻达的异人，钟老先生虽然博闻广见，也未必能全部知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 750,
      "line_end": 752
    }
  ],
